'''歐爾金和諧號'''（MT Orkim Harmony），是一艘[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]籍的[[液貨船|油輪]]<ref name="orkim">{{cite web|url=http://www.marinetraffic.com/ais/details/ships/shipid:707467/mmsi:533042200/imo:9524671/vessel:ORKIM_HARMONY|title=Orkim Harmony|publisher=Marine Traffic|accessdate=24 June 2015|archive-date=2017-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171114202429/http://www.marinetraffic.com/ais/details/ships/shipid:707467/mmsi:533042200/imo:9524671/vessel:ORKIM_HARMONY|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 2015年劫持案 ==
{{main|2015年歐爾金和諧號劫持案}}
2015年6月，這艘船在馬來西亞[[柔佛州|柔佛州]][[哥打丁宜縣|哥打丁宜縣]]丹絨素里里（Tanjung Sedili）附近水域失蹤，其後確認被8名帶著[[手槍|手槍]]與{{link-en|帕兰刀|Parang (knife)}}的{{link-en|印尼海盜|Piracy in Indonesia}}劫持<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/news/asia/south-east-asia/story/mt-orkim-harmony-new-name-same-missing-vessel-20150619|title=MT Orkim Harmony: New name, same missing vessel|publisher=[[The_Straits_Times|The Straits Times]]|date=19 June 2015|accessdate=24 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626160812/http://www.straitstimes.com/news/asia/south-east-asia/story/mt-orkim-harmony-new-name-same-missing-vessel-20150619|dead-url=no}}</ref>。被劫持期間，有22名船員在船上，包括了16名[[馬來西亞人|馬來西亞人]]，5名[[印尼人|印尼人]]，與一名[[緬甸|緬甸]]籍公民<ref name="cna">{{cite web|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/missing-oil-tanker/1917486.html|title=Missing oil tanker probably hijacked by pirates: Malaysian maritime police|author=Melissa Goh|publisher=[[Channel_News_Asia|Channel News Asia]]|date=15 June 2015|accessdate=24 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626131833/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/missing-oil-tanker/1917486.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；船上當時載有6000[[公噸|公噸]]的[[汽油|汽油]]，價值2100萬[[馬來西亞令吉|馬來西亞令吉]]（約合560萬[[美金|美金]]）<ref name="cna"/>。

6月17日，在[[澳大利亚皇家空军|澳大利亚皇家空军]]的協助下，找到這艘船的位置；19日，[[马来西亚皇家海军|马来西亚皇家海军]]、[[马来西亚皇家空军|马来西亚皇家空军]]和{{link-en|馬來西亞海事執法局|Malaysian Maritime Enforcement Agency}}救出了所有[[人質|人質]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-06-18/malaysian-navy-says-missing-tanker-found-in-cambodian-waters/6556942|title=Australian Air Force trails missing Malaysian tanker found in Cambodian waters|publisher=[[Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation|Australian Broadcasting Corporation]]|date=18 June 2015|accessdate=24 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150622001045/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-06-18/malaysian-navy-says-missing-tanker-found-in-cambodian-waters/6556942|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nst.com.my/node/89238|title=EXCLUSIVE: ‘We passed ship the first time’|author1=Farrah Naz Karim|author2=Tasnim Lokman|publisher=[[New_Straits_Times|New Straits Times]]|date=22 June 2015|accessdate=24 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150622090656/http://www.nst.com.my/node/89238|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8名劫船的海盜，被{{link-en|越南邊防隊|Vietnam Border Defense Force}}和[[越南海洋警察司令部|越南海洋警察司令部]]所[[逮捕|逮捕]]，當時他們被發現企圖經過[[越南|越南]]邊境逃跑<ref>{{cite web|url=http://vietnamnews.vn/society/272036/delta-police-nab-pirate-suspects.html|title=Delta police nab pirate suspects|publisher=[[Việt_Nam_News|Việt Nam News]]|date=22 June 2015|accessdate=24 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626111719/http://vietnamnews.vn/society/272036/delta-police-nab-pirate-suspects.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

